      h3 Installing
      p Fortran.io is like PHP: FastCGI runs a script which outputs HTML strings
      h4 Using Ubuntu 14.04
      code sudo apt-get install nginx gfortran spawn-fcgi git libfcgi-dev sqlite3
      br
      code git clone https://github.com/mapmeld/fortran-machine.git
      br
      strong Use gfortran to compile flibs and other libraries, then:
      br
      code spawn-fcgi -a 127.0.0.1 -p 9000 ./fortran_fcgi
